{"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/4GLib14PointerWrapperP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject14GWeakCapturingP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationProtocol"]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","title":"NotificationRef","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:3GIO15NotificationRefV","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"NotificationRef"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"NotificationRef","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"NotificationRef"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The key difference between "},{"code":"GNotification","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and other similar APIs is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that, if supported by the desktop environment, notifications sent","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GNotification"},{"text":" will persist after the application has exited,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and even across system reboots."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since the user may click on a notification while the application is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"not running, applications using ","type":"text"},{"code":"GNotification","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" should be able to be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"started as a D-Bus service, using [class"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In order for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GNotification"},{"type":"text","text":" to work, the application must have installed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".desktop"},{"text":" file. For example:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["[Desktop Entry]","Name=Test Application","Comment=Description of what Test Application does","Exec=gnome-test-application","Icon=org.gnome.TestApplication","Terminal=false","Type=Application","Categories=GNOME;GTK;TestApplication Category;","StartupNotify=true","DBusActivatable=true","X-GNOME-UsesNotifications=true"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"X-GNOME-UsesNotifications","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" key indicates to GNOME Control Center","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that this application uses notifications, so it can be listed in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Control Center’s ‘Notifications’ panel."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".desktop"},{"text":" file must be named as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"org.gnome.TestApplication.desktop"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"where "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"org.gnome.TestApplication"},{"type":"text","text":" is the ID passed to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[ctor"},{"code":"Gio.Application.new","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"User interaction with a notification (either the default action, or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"buttons) must be associated with actions on the application (ie:"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"app."},{"text":" actions).  It is not possible to route user interaction","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"through the notification itself, because the object will not exist if"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the application is autostarted as a result of a notification being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"clicked.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A notification can be sent with [method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.Application.send_notification","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" type acts as a lightweight Swift reference to an underlying ","type":"text"},{"code":"GNotification","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It exposes methods that can operate on this data type through ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationProtocol","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" conformance."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef"},{"text":" only as an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"unowned"},{"type":"text","text":" reference to an existing "},{"code":"GNotification","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Notification"},{"type":"text","text":" (instead of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef","isActive":true},{"text":") if you want to use Automatic Reference Counting for memory management of the underlying ","type":"text"},{"code":"GNotification","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/notificationref"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GNotification"},{"type":"text","text":" is a mechanism for creating a notification to be shown"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to the user — typically as a pop-up notification presented by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"desktop environment shell.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(_:)-4rwii","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(_:)-73m73","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(_:)-8tsd3","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(_:)-9imim","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(_:)-9pvh6","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(cPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(constPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(gconstpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(gpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(mutating:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(opaquePointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/init(title:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/ptr"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/NotificationRef\/unowned(_:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Type Method